comments: Robinson (MIA) and Caruso (LAL) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Caruso (LAL) makes marginal contact with Robinson (MIA) as he is bringing his arm into a vertical position to defend the pass.
Herro (MIA) makes contact to James' (LAL) body and affects his driving shot attempt.
Crowder (MIA) establishes himself in bounds before receiving the pass.
James (LAL) briefly has both hands on Adebayo's (MIA) side before quickly removing them.
Crowder (MIA) rests his hands on Davis' (LAL) back and removes them as he is setting the pick.
Morris (LAL) maintains legal guarding position as contact occurs with Butler (MIA) at the end of the drive.
Butler (MIA) brings both hands to the ball and gathers on his left foot before taking two legal steps prior to starting his upward shooting motion.
Butler (MIA) reaches in from behind and marginal contact occurs with James' (LAL) left side.
Butler's (MIA) right arm is extended slightly forward when contact occurs with James' (LAL) arm/side during the drive, but it is marginal and Butler absorbs it.
Butler (MIA) extends his right arm forward and makes contact to the side of James' (LAL) head that affects his driving shot attempt.
Robinson's (MIA) left hand is extended slightly forward as contact occurs with James' (LAL) right forearm but the contact is marginal.
Morris (LAL) makes contact across Butler's (MIA) left arm after his gather.
Caruso (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Butler's (MIA) path and does not deliver the contact.
Iguodala (MIA) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Butler (MIA) brushes Davis' (LAL) right leg during his upward shooting motion and marginal contact occurs. The release of Davis' shot attempt occurs prior to the expiration of the shot clock.

Crowder (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in James' (LAL) path and gives James room to avoid the contact. Crowder briefly has his left arm placed to James' back before quickly removing it.
Davis (LAL) jumps from point A to point B and initiates body contact with Butler (MIA) during his driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) maintains legal guarding position as contact occurs with James (LAL) near half-court.
Robinson (MIA) moves parallel alongside James' (LAL) path to the basket and makes marginal contact to his side as he makes the pass.
Adebayo (MIA) makes marginal contact with Davis' (LAL) backside as they each attempt to gain rebounding position.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Morris (LAL) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) commits the take foul on Herro (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) jumps to the side of James (LAL) and brushes him as he contests the shot attempt.
